title: Chelsea Clinton Ribs Trump on Sweden: ‘Did They Catch the Bowling Green Massacre Perpetrators?’
text:
Chelsea Clinton Ribs Trump on Sweden: ‘Did They Catch the Bowling Green Massacre Perpetrators?’ by Adam Pribila | 7:44   
Welp, add Chelsea Clinton to the list of people confused/amused by President Trump ‘s comment at Saturday’s campaign (?) rally about an apparent incident “happening last night in Sweden.” What happened in Sweden Friday night? Did they catch the Bowling Green Massacre perpetrators? 
— Chelsea Clinton (@ChelseaClinton) February 19, 2017 
Clinton isn’t the only one to chime in today regarding POTUS’ latest bit of confusion. The Swedish Embassy tweeted to President Trump earlier today asking for clarification on his confounding comments. 
The Commander in Chief would substantiate rumors that what he was referring to was actually just his misunderstanding of a Tucker Carlson segment that aired Friday evening . 
All in all, this seems to confirm suspicions that President Trump’s knowledge — and occasionally opinions — is based on what he sees on Fox News .
